quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  21,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  21,1,logon ka hisaab ( aamaal ka waqt ) nazdeek aap_hncha hai aur woh ghaflat mein ( parre is se ) munh phair rahay hain
  21,2,un ke paas koi nai nasiyaat un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nahi aati magar woh usay khailtay hue suntay hain
  21,3,un ke dil ghaflat mein parre hue hain aur zalim log ( aapas mein ) chupkay chupkay baatein karte hain ke yeh ( shakhs kuch bhi ) nahi magar tumahray jaissa aadmi hai. to tum aankhon dekhte jaadoo ( ki lapait ) mein kyun atay ho
  21,4,( paighambar ne ) kaha ke jo baat aasman aur zameen mein ( kahi jati ) hai mera perwar-digaar usay jaanta hai. aur woh suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  21,5,balkay ( zalim ) kehnay lagey ke ( yeh quran ) pareshan ( baatein hain jo ) khawab ( mein dekh li ) hain. ( nahi ) balkay is ne is ko apni taraf se bana liya hai ( nahi ) balkay ( yeh shair hai jo is ) shayar ( ka tatija ٴ taba ) hai. to jaisay pehlay ( paighambar nishanain day kar ) beje gay they ( isi terhan ) yeh bhi hamaray paas koi nishani laaye
  21,6,un se pehlay jin bustiyon ko hum ne halaakkiya woh imaan nahi latayen theen. tokiya yeh imaan le ayen ge
  21,7,aur hum ne tum se pehlay mard hi ( paighambar bana kar ) beje jin ki taraf hum wahi bhaijtay they. agar tum nahi jantay to jo yaad rakhtay hain un se pooch lau
  21,8,aur hum ne un ke liye aisay jism nahi banaye they ke khana nah khayen aur nah woh hamesha rehne walay they
  21,9,phir hum ne un ke baray mein ( apna ) wada sacha kardiya to un ko aur jis ko chaha nijaat di aur hadd se nikal jaane walon ko halaak kardiya
  21,10,hum ne tumhari taraf aisi kitaab nazil ki hai jis mein tumhara tazkara hai.kiya tum nahi samajte
  21,11,aur hum ne bohat si bustiyon ko jo sitamgar theen halaak kar mara aur un ke baad aur log peda kardiye
  21,12,jab unhon ne hamaray ( muqadma ) azaab ko dekha to lagey is se bhagnay
  21,13,mat bhago aur jin ( nematon ) mein tum aish o aasaish karte they un ki aur apne gharon ki taraf lout jao. shayad tum se ( is baray mein ) daryaftkiya jaye
  21,14,kehnay lagey haae shamat be shak hum zalim they
  21,15,to woh hamesha isi terhan pkarte rahay yahan taq ke hum ne un ko ( khaiti ki terhan ) kaat kar ( aur aag ki terhan ) bujha kar dhair kardiya
  21,16,aur hum ne aasman aur zameen ko jo aur ( makhloqaat ) un dono ke darmain hai is ko لہوولعب ke liye peda nahikiya
  21,17,agar hum chahtay ke khail ( ki cheezein yani zan o farzand ) banayen to agar hum ko karna hota to hum apne paas se bnalite
  21,18,balkay hum sach ko jhoot par khech maartay hain to woh is ka sir toar deta hai aur jhoot isi waqt nabood hojata hai. aur jo baatein tum banatay ho un se tumhari hi kharabi hai
  21,19,aur jo log asmano mein aur jo zameen mein hain sab isi ke ( mamlook aur usi ka maal hain. aur jo ( farishtay ) uss ke paas hain woh is ki ibadat se nah kunyatay(nah sarkashi kartay hain ) hain aur nah uktatay hain
  21,20,raat din ( uss ki ) tasbeeh karte rehtay hain ( nah thakte hain ) nah uktatay hain
  21,21,bhala logon ne jo zameen ki cheezon se ( baaz ko ) mabood bana liya hai ( tokiya ) woh un ko ( marnay ke baad ) uttha khara karen ge ?
  21,22,agar aasman aur zameen mein khuda ke siwa aur mabood hotay to zameen o asmaan darham barham ho jatay. jo baatein yeh log batatay hain khuday-e maalik arsh un se pak hai
  21,23,woh jo kaam karta hai is ki parastish nahi hogi aur ( jo kaam yeh log karte hain is ki ) un se parastish hogi
  21,24,kiya logon ne khuda ko chore kar aur mabood bnalye hain. keh do ke ( is baat par ) apni Daleel paish karo. yeh ( meri aur ) mere sath walon ki kitaab bhi hai aur jo mujh se pehlay ( paighambar ) hue hain. un ki kitaaben bhi hain. balkay ( baat yeh hai ke ) un aksar haq baat ko nahi jantay aur is liye is se munh phair letay hain
  21,25,aur jo paighambar hum ne tum se pehlay beje un ki taraf yahi wahi bhaije ke mere siwa koi mabood nahi to meri hi ibadat karo
  21,26,aur kehte hain ke khuda beta rakhta hai. woh pak hai ( is ke nah beta hai nah beti ) balkay ( jin ko yeh log is ke betay betiyan samajte hain ) woh is ke izzat walay bande hain
  21,27,is ke agay barh kar bol nahi satke. aur is ke hukum par amal karte hain
  21,28,jo kuch un ke agay hochuka hai aur peechay hoga woh sab se waaqif hai aur woh ( is ke paas kisi ki ) sifarish nahi kar saktay magar is shakhs ki jis se khuda khush ho aur woh is ki Haibat se drtay rehtay hain
  21,29,aur jo shakhs un mein se yeh kahe ke khuda ke siwa mein mabood hon to usay hum dozakh ki saza den ge aur zaalmon ko hum aisi hi saza diya karte hain
  21,30,kiya kafiroon ne nahi dekha ke aasman aur zameen dono miley hue they to hum ne judda judda kardiya. aur tamam jandaar cheezein hum ne pani se banayen. phir yeh log imaan kyun nahi laatay ?
  21,31,aur hum ne zameen mein pahar banaye taakay logon ( ke boojh ) se hilnay ( aur jhuknay ) nah lagey aur is mein kushadah rastay banaye taakay log un par chalein
  21,32,aur aasman ko mehfooz chhat banaya. is par bhi woh hamari nshanyon se munh phair rahay hain
  21,33,aur wohi to hai jis ne raat aur din aur Sooraj aur chaand ko banaya. ( yeh ) sab ( yani Sooraj aur chaand aur setaaray ) aasman mein ( is terhan chaltay hain goya ) teer rahay hain
  21,34,aur ( ae paighambar ) hum ne tum se pehlay kisi aadmi ko baqaye Dwam nahi bakhsha. bhala agar tum marjao tokiya yeh log hamesha rahen ge
  21,35,har mutnaqas ko mout ka maza chakhna hai. aur hum to logon ko sakhti aur aasoudgi mein azmaish ke tor par mubtala karte hain. aur tum hamari taraf hi lout kar aao ge
  21,36,aur jab kafir tum ko dekhte hain to tum seistehzaa karte hain kekiya yahi shakhs hai jo tumahray mabodon ka zikar ( buraiee se )kiya karta hai halaank woh khud rehman ke naam se munhkir hain
  21,37,ensaan ( kuch aisa jald baz hai ke goya ) jald baazi hi se banaya gaya hai. mein tum logon ko anqareeb apni nishanain dukhao ga to tum jaldi nah karo
  21,38,aur kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to ( jis azaab ka ) yeh vayd ( hai woh ) kab ( aeye ga ) ?
  21,39,ae kash kafir is waqt ko jaanen jab woh apne monhon par se ( dozakh ki ) aag ko rok nah saken ge aur nah apni pithon par se aur nah un ka koi madadgaar hoga
  21,40,balkay qayamat un par nagahan aa waqay hogi. aur un ke hosh kho day gi. phir nah to woh is ko hata saken ge aur nah un ko mohlat di jaye gi
  21,41,aur tum se pehlay bhi payghambaroon ke sathistehzaa hota raha hai to jo log un mein se tamaskhurkiya karte they un ko isi ( azaab ) ne jis ki hansi uratye they aa ghera
  21,42,kaho ke raat aur din mein khuda se tumhari kon hifazat karsaktha hai? baat yeh hai ke apne perwar-digaar ki yaad se munh phairay hue hain
  21,43,kiya hamaray siwa un ke aur mabood hain ke un ko ( masaaib se ) bacha sakayn. woh aap apni madad to kar hi nahi satke aur nah hum se panah hi diye jayen ge
  21,44,balkay hum un logon ko aur un ke baap dada ko mtmta karte rahay yahan taq ke ( isi haalat mein ) un ki umrein busr hogyin.kiya yeh nahi dekhte ke hum zameen ko is ke kinaroon se ghutatay chalay atay hain. tokiya yeh log ghalba panay walay hain ?
  21,45,keh do ke mein tum ko hukum khuda ke mutabiq nasiyaat karta hon. aur behroon kojb nasiyaat ki jaye to woh pukaar kar suntay hi nahi
  21,46,aur agar un ko tumahray perwar-digaar ka thora sa azaab bhi puhanche to kehnay lagen ke haae kam bakhti hum be shak sitamgar they
  21,47,aur hum qayamat ke din insaaf ki traazo khari karen ge to kisi shakhs ki zara bhi haq talfi nah ki jaye gi. aur agar rai ke danay ke barabar bhi ( kisi ka amal ) hoga to hum is ko la hazir karen ge. aur hum hisaab karne ko kaafi hain
  21,48,aur hum ne moose aur Haroon ko ( hadaayat aur gumraahi mein ) farq kar dainay wali aur ( srtapa ) roshni aur nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) ataa ki ( yani ) parhaiz gaaron ke liye
  21,49,jo ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain aur qayamat ka bhi khauf rakhtay hain
  21,50,yeh mubarak nasiyaat hai jisay hum ne nazil farmaya hai tokiya tum is se inkaar karte ho ?
  21,51,aur hum ne ibrahim ko pehlay hi se hadaayat di thi aur hum un ke haal se waaqif they
  21,52,jab unhon ne apne baap aur apni qoum ke logon se kaha yehkiya moorten hain jin ( ki parastish ) par tum mutakif (o qaa-im ) ho ?
  21,53,woh kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne baap dada ko un ki parastish karte dekha hai
  21,54,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ke tum bhi ( gumraah ho ) aur tumahray baap dada bhi Sarih gumraahi mein parre rahay
  21,55,woh bolaykiya tum hamaray paas ( waqai ) haq laaye ho ya ( hum se ) khail ( ki baatein ) karte ho ?
  21,56,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ( nahi ) balkay tumhara perwar-digaar asmano aur zameen ka perwar-digaar hai jis ne un ko pedakiya hai. aur mein is ( baat ) ka gawah ( aur isi ka qaail ) hon
  21,57,aur khuda ki qasam jab tum peeth phair kar chalay jao ge to mein tumahray buton se aik chaal chaloon ga
  21,58,phir un ko toar kar rezah rezah kardiya magar aik barray ( buut ) ko ( nah tora ) taakay woh is ki taraf rujoo karen
  21,59,kehnay lagey ke hamaray mabodon ke sath yeh maamla kis nekiya? woh to koi zalim hai
  21,60,logon ne kaha ke hum ne aik jawan ko un ka zikar karte hue suna hai is ko ibrahim kehte hain
  21,61,woh bolay ke usay logon ke samnay lao taakay gawah rahen
  21,62,( jab ibrahim aeye to ) buut paraston ne kaha ke ibrahim bhala yeh kaam hamaray mabodon ke sath tum nekiya hai ?
  21,63,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ( nahi ) balkay yeh un ke is barray ( buut ) nekiya ( hoga ). agar yeh boltay hain to un se pooch lau
  21,64,unhon ne apne dil ghhorkiya to aapas mein kehnay lagey be shak tum hi be insaaf ho
  21,65,phir ( sharminda ho kar ) sir neecha karliya ( is par bhi ibrahim se kehnay lagey ke ) tum jantay ho yeh boltay nahi
  21,66,( ibrahim ne ) kaha phir tum khuda ko chore kar kyun aisi cheezon ko pujte ho jo nah tumhe kuch faida day saken aur nuqsaan pouncha saken ?
  21,67,taf hai tum par aur jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho un par bhikiya tum aqal nahi rakhtay ?
  21,68,( tab woh ) kehnay lagey ke agar tumhe ( is se apne mabood ka intiqam lena aur ) kuch karna hai to is ko jala do aur apne mabodon ki madad karo
  21,69,hum ne hukum diya ae aag sard hoja aur ibrahim par ( mojab ) salamti ( ban ja )
  21,70,aur un logon ne bura to un ka chaha tha magar hum ne un hi ko nuqsaan mein daal diya
  21,71,aur ibrahim aur Loot ko is sarzamen ki taraf bacha nikala jis mein hum ne ahal aalam ke liye barket rakhi thi
  21,72,aur hum ne ibrahim ko ashq ataa kiye. aur mstzad bar-aan Yaqoob . aur sab ko naik bakhtkiya
  21,73,aur un ko peshwa banaya ke hamaray hukum se hadaayat karte they aur un ko naik kaam karne aur namaz parhnay aur zakaat dainay ka hukum bheja. aur woh hamari ibadatkiya karte they
  21,74,aur Loot ( ka qissa yaad karo ) jab un ko hum ne hukum ( yani hikmat ونبوت ) aur ilm bakhsha aur is bastii se jahan ke log ganday kaamkiya karte they. bacha nikala. be shak woh buray aur badkirdar log they
  21,75,aur inhen apni rehmat ke ( mehal mein ) daakhilkiya. kuch shak nahi ke woh naik bakhton mein they
  21,76,aur Nooh ( ka qissa bhi yaad karo ) jab ( is se ) peshtar unhon ne hum ko puraka to hum ne un ki dua qubool farmai aur un ko aur un ke sathiyon ko barri ghabrahat se nijaat di
  21,77,aur jo log hamari ayaton ki takzieeb karte they un par nusrat bakhsh. woh be shak buray log they so hum ne un sab ko ghark kardiya
  21,78,aur dawod aur Sulaiman ( ka haal bhi sun lau ke ) jab woh aik khaiti ka muqadma faisla karne lagey jis mein kuch logon ki bakriyan raat ko chur gayi ( aur usay roond gayi ) theen aur hum un ke faislay ke waqt mojood they
  21,79,to hum ne faisla ( karne ka tareeq ) Sulaiman ko samgha diya. aur hum ne dono ko hukum ( yani hikmat o nubuwat ) aur ilm bakhsha tha. aur hum ne pahoron ko dawod ka maskhar kardiya tha ke un ke sath tasbeeh karte they aur janwaron ko bhi ( maskhar kardiya tha aur hum hi aisa ) karne walay they
  21,80,aur hum ne tumahray liye un ko aik ( terhan ) ka libaas banana bhi sikha diya taakay tum ko larai ( ke zarrar ) se bachaaye. pas tum ko shukar guzar hona chahiye
  21,81,aur hum ne taiz howa Sulaiman ke tabay ( farmaan ) kar di thi jo un ke hukum se is malik mein chalti thi jis mein hum ne barket di thi ( yani shaam ) aur hum har cheez se khabardaar hain
  21,82,aur dewoon ( ki jamaat ko bhi un ke tabay kardiya tha ke un ) mein se baaz un ke liye ghote maartay they aur is ke siwa aur kaam bhi karte they aur hum un ke nigehbaan they
  21,83,aur ayub ko ( yaad karo ) jab unhon ne apne perwar-digaar se dua ki ke mujhe aeza ho rahi hai aur to sab se barh kar reham karne wala hai
  21,84,to hum ne un ki dua qubool karli aur jo un ko takleef thi woh daur kar di aur un ko baal bachay bhi ataa farmaiye aur apni meharbani ke sath itnay hi aur ( bakhshay ) aur ibadat karne walon ke liye ( yeh ) nasiyaat hai
  21,85,aur asmayl aur adrees aur zulkaffal ( ko bhi yaad karo ) yeh sab sabr karne walay they
  21,86,aur hum ne un ko apni rehmat mein daakhilkiya. bilashuba woh nekokaar they
  21,87,aur Zulnun ( ko yaad karo ) jab woh ( apni qoum se naraaz ho kar ) ghusse ki haalat mein chal diye aur khayaalkiya ke hum un par qaboo nahi paskin ge. aakhir andheray mein ( khuda ko ) pukarnay lagey ke tairay siwa koi mabood nahi. to pak hai ( aur ) be shak mein qasoorwar hon
  21,88,to hum ne un ki dua qubool karli aur un ko gham se nijaat bakhsh. aur imaan walon ko hum isi terhan nijaat diya karte hain
  21,89,aur zikria ( ko yaad karo ) jab unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ko puraka ke perwar-digaar mujhe akela nah chore aur to sab se behtar waris hai
  21,90,to hum ne un ki pukaar sun li. aur un ko yahya bakhshay aur un ki biwi ko unn ke ( husn muashrat ke ) qabil banadiya. yeh log lapak lapak kar naikian karte aur hamein umeed se pkarte aur hamaray agay aajzikiya karte they
  21,91,aur un ( maryam ) ko ( bhi yaad karo ) jinhon ne apni iffat ko mehfooz rakha. to hum ne un mein apni rooh phoonk di aur un ke betay ko ahal aalam ke liye nishani bana diya
  21,92,yeh tumhari jamaat aik hi jamaat hai aur mein tumhara perwar-digaar hon to meri hi ibadatkiya karo
  21,93,aur yeh log apne muamlay mein baahum mutafarraq hogaye. ( magar ) sab hamari taraf rujoo karne walay hain
  21,94,jo naik kaam kere ga aur momin bhi hoga to is ki koshish raaygan nah jaye gi. aur hum is ke liye ( sawab aamaal ) likh rahay hain
  21,95,aur jis bastii ( walon ) ko hum ne halaak kardiya mahaal hai ke ( woh duniya ki taraf rujoo karen ) woh rujoo nahi karen ge
  21,96,yahan taq ke yajooj majooj khol diye jayen aur woh har bulandi se daud rahay hon
  21,97,aur ( qayamat ka ) sacha wada qareeb aajay to nagah kafiroon ki ankhen khuli ki khuli reh jayen ( aur kehnay lagen ke ) haae shamat hum is ( haal ) se ghaflat mein rahay balkay ( apne haq mein ) zalim they
  21,98,( kafroo is roz ) tum aur jin ki tum khuda ke siwa ibadat karte ho dozakh ka eendhan hon ge. aur tum sab is mein daakhil ho kar raho ge
  21,99,agar yeh log ( dar haqeeqat ) mabood hotay to is mein daakhil nah hotay. sab is mein hamesha ( jaltay ) rahen ge
  21,100,wahan un ko chalana hoga aur is mein ( kuch ) nah sun saken ge
  21,101,jin logon ke liye hamari taraf se pehlay bhalai muqarrar hochuki hai. woh is se daur rakhay jayen ge
  21,102,( yahan taq ke ) is ki aawaz bhi to nahi sunen ge. aur jo kuch un ka jee chahay ga is mein ( yani ) har terhan ke aish aur lutaf mein hamesha rahen ge
  21,103,un ko ( is din ka ) bara bhaari khauf ghamgeen nahi kere ga. aur farishtay un ko lainay ayen ge ( aur kahin ge ke ) yahi woh din hai jis ka tum se wadakiya jata hai
  21,104,jis din hum aasman ko is terhan lapait len ge jaisay khitton ka tomaar lapait letay hain. jis terhan hum ne ( kaayenaat ko ) pehlay pedakiya isi terhan dobarah peda kar dein ge. ( yeh ) wada ( jis ka poora karna lazim ) hai. hum ( aisa ) zaroor karne walay hain
  21,105,aur hum ne nasiyaat ( ki kitaab yani torat ) ke baad Zaboor mein likh diya tha ke mere nekokaar bande malik ke waris hon ge
  21,106,ibadat karne walay logon ke liye is mein ( khuda ke hukmon ki ) tableegh hai
  21,107,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko tamam Jahan ke liye rehmat ( bana kar ) bheja hai
  21,108,keh do ke mujh par ( khuda ki taraf se ) yeh wahi aati hai ke tum sab ka mabood khuday-e wahid hai. to tum ko chahiye ke farmanbardar ban jao
  21,109,agar yeh log munh phairen to keh do ke mein ne tum ko sab ko yaksaa ( ehkaam Ellahi se ) aagah kardiya hai. aur mujh ko maloom nahi ke jis cheez ka tum se wadakiya jata hai woh ( an ) qareeb ( anay wali ) hai ya ( is ka waqt ) daur hai
  21,110,aur jo baat pukaar ki jaye woh usay bhi jaanta hai aur jo tum posheeda karte ho is se bhi waaqif hai
  21,111,aur mein nahi jaanta shayad woh tumahray liye azmaish ho aur aik muddat taq ( tum is se ) faida ( uthatay raho )
  21,112,paighambar ne kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar haq ke sath faisla kardey. aur hamara perwar-digaar bara meharban hai isi se un baton mein jo tum bayan karte ho madad mangi jati hai
